mesa
------------------------------------------
X11 OpenGL libraries

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.0-62
  libgcc1-4.3.4-1
  libstdc++6-4.3.4-1
  libX11_6-1.3-1
  libXext6-1.1-1
  libXm2-0.95.2-1
  libXt6-1.0.7-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-2.19.51-1
  cygport-0.9.10-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.4-1
  gcc4-g++-4.3.4-1
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23b-10
  sed-4.1.5-2
  glproto-1.4.10-1
  libGLEW-devel-1.5.1-10
  libglut-devel-2.4.0-1

Canonical website:
  http://mesa3d.org/

Canonical download:
  ftp://ftp.freedesktop.org/pub/mesa/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mesa-7.5.2-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mesa-7.5.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mesa-7.5.2-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mesa-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL-devel-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGL1-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU-devel-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLU1-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw-devel-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libGLw1-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOSMesa-devel-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOSMesa7-7.5.2-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

